column2: SELECT TOP # manu.specObjID, manu.z, pz.z as photoz       FROM PhotoObjAll            AS p,      Photoz                 AS pz,      MyDB.manu_DR1#_matched AS manu    WHERE p.ObjID = manu.ObjID AND      pz.ObjID = manu.ObjID AND     zoo.ObjID = manu.ObjID AND        manu.z < #     ORDER BY manu.SpecObjID
